_sText: Didn't have any plans to make anything else but a friend requested that I make a map for him in the style of bhop_quickie so here it is, around 1:05 for a good nofail run, designed to be one shot although each stage can be done from the starting 250 units, with maybe a little pre-speeding required towards the later stages. I hate rectangular/boxy rooms typically but since it was an easy request to fulfil why not.
